 <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">The ambient temperature stress is applied to the system under test by a dynamic climate chamber.</p>
 <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">The temperature of the chamber is set to change from −40 °C to +60 °C by a step of 
  <div class="inline-formula">
   <div id="mm109" class="math">
    <div class="mrow">
     <div class="mrow">
      <span class="mo">Δ</span>
      <span class="mi">T</span>
     </div>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>. The four-quadrant PIN detector and the post-processing circuit are kept for 
  <div class="inline-formula">
   <div id="mm110" class="math">
    <div class="mrow">
     <div class="mrow">
      <div class="msub">
       <span class="mi">t</span>
       <div class="mrow">
        <span class="mi">h</span>
        <span class="mi">o</span>
        <span class="mi">l</span>
        <span class="mi">d</span>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div> at a certain ambient temperature in order to ensure that the temperature of the device under test(DUT) is stable. The slope of temperature change 
  <div class="inline-formula">
   <div id="mm111" class="math">
    <div class="mrow">
     <div class="mrow">
      <div class="msub">
       <span class="mi">K</span>
       <span class="mi">T</span>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div> is set to 5 °C/min to avoid the thermal shock to the DUT. The setting curve of the dynamic climate chamber is shown in 
  <a ref-type="fig" rid="sensors-19-02284-f005" href="#sensors-19-02284-f005">Figure 5</a>, where 
  <div class="inline-formula">
   <div id="mm112" class="math">
    <div class="mrow">
     <div class="mrow">
      <span class="mo">Δ</span>
      <span class="mi">T</span>
     </div>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div> is 5 °C and 
  <div class="inline-formula">
   <div id="mm113" class="math">
    <div class="mrow">
     <div class="mrow">
      <div class="msub">
       <span class="mi">t</span>
       <div class="mrow">
        <span class="mi">h</span>
        <span class="mi">o</span>
        <span class="mi">l</span>
        <span class="mi">d</span>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div> is 20 min.
 </p>
